familyMemberEthics.description: Jared Kushner served as Non-member Manager of DJNJ Frito, LLC from Jan 1, 2011, to Jan 1, 2017. Jared Kushner received 17375 in Brokerage commissions income from DJNJ FRITO, LLC (Insurance brokerage license; Florham Park, NJ) the year before his appointment as Pres. Trump's senior adviser. Because his interest in this entity reportedly has been divested, the potential conflict of interest is marked in this database as resolved.
